Violet Graham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Violet_Graham 0 Violet Graham (1890–1967) was an English stage and film actress. Graham played leading roles in several films of the silent era, often appearing in those of the director Sidney Morgan such as Auld Lang Syne. Graham was in the original cast of the 1909 musical The Arcadians. Violet_Graham ( 1890 – 1967 ) was an_English_stage_and_film_actress .
